text: "I Don't Want to Spoil the Party" is a 1965 song by The Beatles and is the B-side from their single Eight Days a Week. It went to number 39 in the United States. ==Rosanne Cash version== In 1989, Rosanne Cash recorded a cover of I Don't Want to Spoil the Party for her compilation Hits 1979-1989. It went to number 1 in the country charts in the United States and Canada. ==References== Category:The Beatles songs Category:1965 songs Category:Country rock songs Category:Rosanne Cash songs
title: I Don't Want to Spoil the Party
